### Calling construct reference

```java
@FuctionalInterface
interface Teller{
    String tellName(String name);
}

public class MyClass{
    public static void main(String[] args){
        Teller methodRef = String::new;// s -> new String
        System.out.println(methodRef.tellName("John Wayne"));
    }
}
```

